            <div style="background: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #2e7d32;">Potential Savings:</div>
                <div id="modalSavings" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #2e7d32;"></div>
                <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #388e3c;">vs PayPal on this transfer</div>
